---
// Terms of Service
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 8, 2026';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - GuildPost"
  description="Read the Terms of Service for GuildPost. Learn about our policies, user responsibilities, and guidelines for using our Minecraft server listing platform."
  url="https://guildpost.tech/terms"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0f]">
    <Header />
    
    <main class="pt-20 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">Terms of Service 📋</h1>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0]">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-[#8892b0] max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-[#8892b0] mb-8">
            Welcome to GuildPost! By using our website, you agree to these Terms of Service. Please read them carefully. If you don't agree, please don't use our services.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            By accessing or using GuildPost ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access the Service.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            GuildPost is a platform that allows users to discover, list, and share Minecraft servers. We provide tools for server owners to promote their servers and for players to find new servers to join.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            When you create an account with us, you must provide accurate and complete information. You are responsible for safeguarding your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Create multiple accounts for abusive purposes</li>
            <li>Share your account credentials with others</li>
            <li>Use another person's account without permission</li>
            <li>Engage in fraudulent voting or manipulation</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Server Listings</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            When submitting a server to GuildPost, you confirm that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>You have the right to list the server</li>
            <li>The server information is accurate and not misleading</li>
            <li>The server does not violate Minecraft's EULA or our content guidelines</li>
            <li>You will maintain the server and keep information up-to-date</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Prohibited Content</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Servers and content that are NOT allowed on GuildPost include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Hate speech, harassment, or discrimination</li>
            <li>Illegal activities or content</li>
            <li>Malware, viruses, or harmful software</li>
            <li>Pornographic or sexually explicit content</li>
            <li>Scams, phishing, or fraudulent schemes</li>
            <li>Servers promoting violence or terrorism</li>
            <li>Copyright-infringing content without permission</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Voting System</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Our voting system is designed to be fair and accurate. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Vote only once per server per cooldown period (typically 24 hours)</li>
            <li>Not use bots, scripts, or automated tools to vote</li>
            <li>Not attempt to manipulate vote counts</li>
            <li>Accept that we may remove fraudulent votes without notice</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. Premium Services</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Premium and Elite subscriptions are billed on a recurring basis. You can cancel at any time. Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis within 14 days of purchase if the service wasn't used.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            GuildPost and its original content are the property of GuildPost. You retain ownership of your server listings and content, but grant us a license to display and promote them on our platform.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Minecraft is a trademark of Mojang Studios. We are not affiliated with Mojang or Microsoft.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">9. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            We may terminate or suspend your account and access to the Service immediately, without prior notice, for any reason including breach of these Terms. Upon termination, your right to use the Service will immediately cease.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">10. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee the accuracy of server information, uptime, or availability. Use of servers listed on our platform is at your own risk.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            GuildPost shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your use of or inability to use the Service.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will notify users of significant changes via email or through the Service. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@guildpost.tech" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">legal@guildpost.tech</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[#2a2a3a]">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/privacy" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
            <span class="text-[#2a2a3a]">|</span>
            <a href="/dmca" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">DMCA Policy</a>
            <span class="text-[#2a2a3a]">|</span>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
